<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
	<title>Spreen - The Screen Sharing App</title>
	<!-- CSS only -->
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/jpg" href="./assets/favicon.png" />

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" />
	<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
		integrity="sha384-giJF6kkoqNQ00vy+HMDP7azOuL0xtbfIcaT9wjKHr8RbDVddVHyTfAAsrekwKmP1" crossorigin="anonymous" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="./assets/css/style.css" />
</head>

<body>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="center">
			<h1>FEATURES</h1>
		</div>

		<p id="my-id"></p>
		<br />
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm center">
				<div>
					<div class="feature-img center">
						<img src="./assets/easytouse.png" alt="" />
					</div>
					<h3>Easy to Use</h3>
				</div>
				<h5 class="feature-desc">
					Just follow the guidelines on the
					<a href="https://github.com/IshaanOhri/Spreen" target="_blank"
						style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(74, 45, 200)">GitHub</a>
					repository as to how to start the Spreen server and then follow the on screen instructions.
				</h5>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm center">
				<div>
					<div class="feature-img center">
						<img src="./assets/fast.png" alt="" />
					</div>
					<h3>Fast</h3>
				</div>
				<h5 class="feature-desc">
					As Spreen shares content over a local network, it provides the best user experience with minimum
					latency and
					maximum quality.
				</h5>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm center">
				<div>
					<div class="feature-img center">
						<img src="./assets/nointernet.png" alt="" />
					</div>
					<h3>No Cables. No Internet</h3>
				</div>
				<h5 class="feature-desc">
					The two devices are not required to be connected via cable or over the internet. They just need to
					be
					connected to the same local network.
				</h5>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm center">
				<div>
					<div class="feature-img center">
						<img src="./assets/restrictsharing.png" alt="" />
					</div>
					<h3>Restrict Sharing</h3>
				</div>
				<h5 class="feature-desc">Share your entire screen or just a single window, the choice is totally yours.
				</h5>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm center">
				<div>
					<div class="feature-img center">
						<img src="./assets/anyscreen.png" alt="" />
					</div>
					<h3>Any Screen</h3>
				</div>
				<h5 class="feature-desc">Use any additional device with a web browser as a second screen.</h5>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm center">
				<div>
					<div class="feature-img center">
						<img src="./assets/free.png" alt="" />
					</div>
					<h3>Free</h3>
				</div>
				<h5 class="feature-desc">Spreen is an open source project and is therefore completely FREE.</h5>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<button id="share-btn" class="float">
		<i class="fa fa-desktop fa-lg"></i>
	</button>

	<div id="myModal" class="modal">
		<!-- Modal content -->
		<div class="modal-content">
			<span class="close">&times;</span>
			<div class="center">
				<p>Make sure your computer and device are connected to the same network</p>
				<p>Scan the QR code</p>
				<img id="barcode"
					src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?data=<%= baseurl %>/watch&amp;size=100x100" alt=""
					title="HELLO" width="50" height="50" />
				<br />
				<br />
				<p>or type the following address manually in the address bar:</p>
				<a href="<%= baseurl %>/watch" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none">
					<p id="ip-add" class="center">
						<%= baseurl %>/watch
					</p>
				</a>
				<p><i>Ensure you connect to the client before starting the screen share</i></p>
				<p id="client-status" class="center">Waiting for client to connect</p>
			</div>
			<div id="video-grid"></div>
			<div class="center">
				<button id="start-share" onclick="shareScreen()">Start Screen Share</button>
				&nbsp; &nbsp;
				<button id="stop-share" disabled>Stop Screen Share</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<a href="https://github.com/IshaanOhri/Spreen" target="_blank" style="color: white">
		<button id="share-btn" class="github share"><i class="fa fa-github fa-2x" aria-hidden="true"></i></button></a>
</body>

<script src="https://unpkg.com/peerjs@1.3.1/dist/peerjs.min.js"></script>
<script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
<script src="./js/home.js"></script>

</html>